DAY 5 — SHELL & SCRIPTING
-------------------------
Introduction
-------------
Shell is a command-line interface to interact with OS.
* Executes commands
* Interacts with OS

Variables
---------
name="Rekha"
echo $name
  
Input/Output
------------
> → overwrite
>> → append

Conditions
----------
if [ $a -gt 10 ]; then
 echo "Greater"
fi
  
Loops
-----
for i in {1..10}
do
 echo $i
done
